The paper discusses a correction to Gallager's capacity theorem for waveform channels, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT). The correction involves waveform channels, which are a type of signal processing and communication system, and may fall under the sub-category of signal processing (cs.SI). The correction may also involve the use of machine learning or statistical techniques to improve the capacity theorem, which could fall under the sub-categories of multimedia (cs.MM), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), or machine learning (cs.LG).
